{"a":1, "b":2, "c":3, "d":"c"}
}}}
EXPECTED = {{{
{"a":1, "b":2, "c":1, "e":2}
}}}
SKIP=object keys are compile-time-constant strings in this engine; no way to compute a key at render time.

