}}}
EXPECTED = {{{
[[1,[[2]],{"a":[1]}],1,[[2]],[2],2,{"a":[1]},[1],1]
}}}
SKIP=no recursive-descent operator; even $pyrun's statement support doesn't give you unbounded structural recursion for free without real effort.

